title: SAVINGS here!! Move-in to your 2BR NOW, Amazing location, Enjoy patio
posting_body: ['The Elliott Pointe Apartments offers unique studio, one and two bedroom floor plans to suit your desire for luxury apartment living.', 'Our apartments feature fantastic designer-colored walls, luxury plank floor, and stainless steel kitchen appliances.', 'This apartment features:', 'Private patio & deck w/Storage!', 'Overlooking pool & courtyard', 'Wood-flooring throughout', 'Walk-in Closet', 'Cozy fireplace and loads of closet space', 'Great for roommates', 'Large deck & private patio', 'Full-size Washer/Dryer', 'Come Visit us!', 'Elliott Pointe', '2226 Elliott Avenue', 'Seattle, WA 98121', '<URL>', 'Contact us today to schedule a tour!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'Office Hours -- Come visit us for more information and tours!', 'Monday – Friday', '9:00am – 6:00pm', 'Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.', 'related search terms ::: Elliott Bay, Pike Place Market, Seattle Waterfront, Bell Street Bridge, Belltown, Seattle Art Institute, highway 5, highway 99, Pier 66']
